  <div slot="season-info">
    <p>The Fall League runs September through late October, weather permitting. Open to all skill levels.</p>

    <h4 class="red">Handicap order: 5, 6, 2, 7, 3, 9, 4, 8, 1</h4>

    <h4 class="red">Tee Box Color / Attire</h4>
    <p>
      September 3 – White Tee / Hawaiian Shirt<br />
      September 10 – Black Tee / Red-White-Blue patriotic shirt for 9/11<br />
      September 17 – White Tee / Blue Shirt<br />
      September 24 – Black Tee / Yellow Shirt and or "Flat Hat"<br />
      October 1 – White Tee / Orange Shirt<br />
      October 8 – Black Tee / Red Shirt<br />
      October 15 – White Tee / NFL, MLB, NBA Attire<br />
      October 22 – Black Tee / Black Shirt<br />
      October 29 – Black Tee / Halloween Costume, Camo or Blaze Orange Attire
    </p>

    <h4>Contact</h4>
    <p>For more information, call <a href="tel:920-779-6421">(920) 779-6421</a>.</p>
